"Do these make funny shapes ?"
"Well, No. Unless you think round is funny".

The o.d. doesn't have to be any larger than the MC flange.
( Any more is just wasted :).
The MC is stepped at the flange, but a single slightly larger 
hole which allows the boot to install normally will work fine.
The relevent dimensional question is:
How thick is it ?
